quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,"Amai ka so Langit na manga bubungkag,"
  82,2,"Go amai ka so manga Bito-on na mikayambur,"
  82,3,"Go amai ka so manga Kalo­dan na Pakandadanona-an,"
  82,4,"Go amai ka so manga kobor na pamaklidun,"
  82,5,"Na katokawan o ginawa so piyakaona niyan a go so piyakaori niyan."
  82,6,"Hai Manosiya! Antona-a i Miyakalimpang ruka ko Kadnan ka, a Maginawa,"
  82,7,"So Miyadun Ruka , go Mithaong Ruka phiyapiya, go mis­hokod ruka?"
  82,8,"Apiya antona-a bontal i ka­ baya lyan na Piyakimbontal lyan Ruka."
  82,9,"Sabunar, a kuna, ka o Ongkir­un niyo so Kokoman!"
  82,10,"A Mata-an! A titho a adun a khisisiyap rukano (a manga Malai­kat),-"
  82,11,"A Khisusula-an, -a manga Panonorat:"
  82,12,"A katawan niran so gi-i niyo nggolaola-an."
  82,13,"Mata-an! A so Miyamara­tiyaya, na khatago dun ko Pakadar­andang."
  82,14,"Na Mata-an! A so manga baradosa na khatago dun ko Nar­aka Jahim;"
  82,15,"Phamakasolud siran non ko Alongan a kapamalas,"
  82,16,"Na di siran non mamaka­awa."
  82,17,"Na antawa-a i miyakandao Ruka o antona-a i Alongan a kapa­malas?"
  82,18,"Oriyan niyan, na antawa-a i miyakandao Ruka o antona-a i Alongan a kapamalas?"
  82,19,"So Alongan a da-a mapukha­ pa-ar o isa a ginawa ko isa a ginawa a maito bo: Ka so Kokoman sa Alongan noto, na Ruk o Allah ."
